# ============================================
# Google Antigravity - AI Agentic IDE
# ============================================
# Strategy Group: PayPal (ISP California)
# Purpose: Route Antigravity to US ISP nodes
# Reason: US Gmail account region authentication
#         requires clean US residential/ISP IP.
#         Google OAuth geo-check is strict enough
#         that datacenter IPs (OIX) can mismatch.
#
# Rule placement: MUST load before google.list
# in Surge [Rule] section — these domains are
# subsets of google.list catch-alls and require
# earlier matching to redirect to ISP group.
#
# IMPORTANT: Antigravity does NOT follow macOS
# system proxy settings. Surge Enhanced Mode
# (TUN) is required for rules to take effect.
# ============================================

# > Core App & OAuth Callback
# antigravity.google TLD is caught by DOMAIN-KEYWORD,google
# in google.list — must override here first.
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,antigravity.google

# > Primary AI API Endpoint
# Source: elad12390/antigravity-proxy — confirmed internal
# CloudCode sandbox endpoint, NOT the public Gemini API.
DOMAIN,daily-cloudcode-pa.sandbox.googleapis.com

# > Cloud AI Companion API (IAM auth path)
# Source: NoeFabris/opencode-antigravity-auth issue #191
# "Permission 'cloudaicompanion.companions.generateChat' denied"
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cloudaicompanion.googleapis.com

# > Extension Registry
# Source: discuss.ai.google.dev login thread — user-confirmed whitelist
# Antigravity uses OpenVSX instead of Microsoft's marketplace.
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,open-vsx.org

# > VS Code Infrastructure (Antigravity is a VS Code fork)
# Note: unverified via official docs — included conservatively.
# These do NOT require US IP; routed here for group consistency.
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vscode-cdn.net
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,vsassets.io
